ABOUT US

USA Crypto Group is a leading provider in cryptocurrency research, analysis and hosting AMAs. We connect developers and their projects  to investors. 

USA Crypto Group started by 50x Godfather and a handful of crypto currency enthusiasts in search for the next upcoming and hot projects to invest into. Through research and analysis, USA Crypto Group has brought several projects to its community members with the ROI of over 20x of invested money! USA Crypto Group now has grown internationally with members all over the world and is now one of the most popular groups for developers to present and introduce  their projects to investors, as well as a place where crypto enthusiasts like to hang out, share and discuss everything related to cryptocurrency.
